title: YouTube Is For Everyone, Love It!
text: I get the best suggestions on my YouTube feed, they are great about paying attention to what you like and what you want to see, what do you want or need to know. The information, if you know where to search and find channels you trust, Is always very accurate and so quick and easy to find! I keep an eye on things because I have a child, so I appreciate the way they do filter a bit and warn you if something is explicit or in someway shocking. Overall I pretty much live on getting My Info/ & Entertainment from YouTube and don’t know what I would do without it now in 2024!

title: Buffering problem. Please get rid of it, Google! 😵‍💫👎
text: So, the reason why I am giving this app three stars (⭐️⭐️⭐️) is because I have been noticing that whenever I watch my favorite YouTube videos, they start to buffer for a couple of seconds before starting again, but then it just happens again seconds faster than the speed of light! 😮 Omg, this is like super duper annoying, you should totally get rid of this issue, and also find out the issue on why this happens. 🫥 It’s also starting to annoy me the more I see this kind of issue. 🥴 So, again I tell you, the sooner you get rid of this buffering problem in this YouTube app, the sooner I’ll be happy and amazed, and then to give this app five stars (⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️) next time I review this app! 😎👍
